    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## How it works?\n1. Scrapes past content ideas from Google Sheets.\n2. Detects underused content categories (e.g. case studies, growth hacks).\n3. Uses Claude 3.7 to generate a new idea, post text, and image description.\n4. Crafts a custom prompt and sends it to OpenAI‚Äôs image model to generate a matching visual.\n5. Stores everything (idea, text, image) in Google Sheets.\n6. Once marked as \"ready\", it downloads the image and auto-publishes to LinkedIn via API.\n",
        "height": 344,
        "width": 320,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "cffa9c18-966d-4a81-adf1-2eb3f1a38a3c",
