    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## What does it do?\nObjective: Automatically generate LinkedIn posts with engaging content and visuals based on least-used content buckets. Each post includes a powerful hook, image, and text ‚Äî all written by AI, scheduled, and optionally published.\n\n### Why important?\n- Stop staring at a blank screen ‚Äî AI brainstorms for you.\n- Ensure content variety using intelligent bucket rotation.\n- Save time and maintain high-quality, daily posting cadence.\n\nWhether you're a solopreneur, content team, or agency ‚Äî this system builds a consistent LinkedIn presence while you sleep.\n",
        "height": 504,
