      "parameters": {
        "content": "\n## Tokens Required\n- Claude (Anthropic)\n- OpenAI (image generation)\n- Google Sheets + Drive\n- LinkedIn \n- Facebook/Instagram (optional)\n\n## Scalability\n- Easily expand for Twitter, Instagram, or Threads.\n- Add more content buckets or modify posting rules (e.g. twice daily).\n- Swap LinkedIn for other platforms by changing publishing nodes.",
